{"tid":1514311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住，係敵退我進，唔係敵退我退","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:42:14.000Z","uid":33307,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e897900d47b45fd36da28829d5d0314654c97eb5","tid":1514311,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"敵退我退，即係返去6月8號<br />\n損兵折將，一無所獲，聽日又裝返燈柱，繼續150，一簽多行，普教中，國教，清算示威人士，炒黃絲，大搜捕，庫房直接送中，垃圾基建<br />\n<br />\n仲有泉下七個手足<br />\n900個被捕，隨時被清算既義士<br />\n獄中梁天琦魚革80義士一等人<br />\n比國泰炒既手足<br />\n<br />\n全部都要還返晒比對家，直至佢哋完全潰敗"},{"pid":"314f9dbd06d8ed2fab1ae63547c73ca4a50f359d","tid":1514311,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"停止抗爭，就會被反撲，被消滅"},{"pid":"c281194bd3056d1f1f6865e083a525b264bd5681","tid":1514311,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ae265e51bd2b6764265ed699e1a9150dbe098f9b","tid":1514311,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e40fd595ee00f93f0e112e26f679681c0b11c2b1","tid":1514311,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1527a787a26eaf7ef60a7a229647a3c864ff10ee","tid":1514311,"uid":127085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:00:16.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"b5887187736137b5224675a33008b68da988141f","tid":1514311,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:39:18.000Z","msg":"831 中聯辦"},{"pid":"4efd5745addb8bee6a7259c769376b3f80699802","tid":1514311,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"dc6ec6db22c2a016deed1b332c2d31b5324ab51b","tid":1514311,"uid":182997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"831"}]}